message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech separation, which is a subfield of audio signal processing. cs.CL is also likely as the paper evaluates the separation performance on a speech recognition task. cs.LG is another possible category as the paper discusses the optimization of separation criterion in frequency-domain networks. cs.SI and cs.MM are less likely but still possible categories as the paper incorporates spatial and speaker location information in the development of multi-channel solutions.
